pdl-winnt CHANGELOG
-------------------

0.1.0
  + initial with April 2008

0.1.1
  + unattended: embed serial key
  + unattended: set timezone

0.1.2
  + update: add KB898461 to KB981793
  + addons: firefox 3.6.3
  + run_once: remove firefox desktop icon
  + extras: common drivers, adobe-reader-8.20, cccp-2009-09-09, ccleaner-2.32,
