    pidgin-2.7.0, utorrent-2.02

0.1.3
  + new base iso "biexpp111" January 2011
  + addons: 7zip-9.20, cccp-10.10.2010, firefox-3.6.13, gimp-2.6.11,
    infrarecorder-0.51, inkscape-0.48, pidgin-2.7.9
  + remove: web folders
  + use classic login
  + include: internet explorer (8), intel indeo codecs, scanner drivers
  + unattended: revert "programs" directory to "Program Files"
  + unattended: change default root password
  + unattended: set automatic update to "notify before download"
  + runonce: remove all *.lnk files on desktop
  + runonce: move games into accessories
  + runonce: deleting "programs\ComPlus Applications" is no longer necessary
  + start menu: enable "My Network Places" as a link
  + start menu: remove windows update shortcut
  + readme with instructions in extra
  + extras: only clamwin-0.96.5, evince-2.30.3, gedit-2.30.1-1, gsrync-0.6.3,
    libreoffice-3.3.0rc4, utorrent 2.2

0.1.4
  + start with new iso "biexpp411" April 2011
  + addons: firefox-4.0, infrarecorder-0.52, inkscape 0.48.1, jre-6.25,
    pidgin-2.7.11, putty-0.6.0
  + include: mouse cursors, windows media player
  + remove: help and support, alerter service, application layer gateway service
  + runonce: clean up, move infrarecorder to programs
  + tweaks: enable cursor shadow, accept privacy statement,
    disable auto-add music to library, disable automatic codec download,
    disable metadata retrieval, disable MRU, disable silent acquisition,
    disable starting with media guide, enhanced privacy settings,
    remove all context menu entries
  + services: disable distributed transaction coordinator, smart card,
    terminal services, themes
  + extras: clamwin-0.97, evince-2.32.0, libreoffice-3.3.2, netframework-2.0_SP1
    nlite-1.4.9.1, utorrent-2.2.1
